===Excuse me, is this...===
{{Messages
|start_condition = 
|text =
:'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Excuse me, is this the deceased {{MC|m=Mr.|f=Miss}} (Trailblazer)'s number?
:{Choice} You want me deceased?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm very much alive, thanks.
:{Choice} What the heck...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Deceased!? What the heck...
:'''Mr. Xiyan:''' My apologies. I meant "the distinguished." This autocorrect is a little morbid...
:'''Mr. Xiyan:''' You're a hero of the Xianzhou. I worked hard to get your contact details.
:'''Mr. Xiyan:''' In fact, I have some private matter I'm hoping you can help with. I hope it won't be too much trouble.
:{Choice} It'll be no trouble
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I've heard you tell stories a lot when I went past the tea house. I'd be honored to be able to help you
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Oh, you flatter me
:{Choice} What's the pay?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sir, you should know that time is money
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' That I am well aware. I will prepare sufficient compensation.
:'''Mr. Xiyan:''' I usually tell stories on the stage before the Sleepless Earl. You can find me there to discuss this issue face-to-face.
;{Accepted Mission: Tales of the Fantastic: Chapter 1}
}}
