:'''Mr. Xiyan:''' {{MC|f=Ms.|m=Mr.}} (Trailblazer), I recently received a pet &mdash; a fun creature &mdash; from an avid listener. I thought you might be interested.
:'''Mr. Xiyan:''' I can't bring it with me when I'm telling stories, so I've left it at Spare Time Book Shop, which is my store.
:'''Mr. Xiyan:''' If you're interested, you can drop by Spare Time Book Shop and take a look. I believe you'll like it!
:{Choice} Yeah, I'm interested.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' A pet? I adore small animals. Let me check it out now.
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Heheh, I'm sure you've never seen the animal before. It's very fascinating.
:{Choice} I'm not interested.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm not really keen on it... As a Trailblazer, I'm too busy to check out a pet.
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Don't jump to conclusions so soon! I'm sure you've never seen the animal before. It's very fascinating.
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Go ahead and take a look when you change your mind.
;{Accepted Mission: Youci's Clever Decor}
